1. *Peva* mi se pesma koju si mi juče pokazao. (I'm singing the song you showed me yesterday.)
2. On *peva* u horu već pet godina. (He has been singing in the choir for five years.)
3. Kada *pevam*, osećam se srećno. (When I sing, I feel happy.)
4. Oni *pevaju* nacionalnu himnu svaki put kada pobede. (They sing the national anthem every time they win.)
5. Kada je ona u društvu, uvek *peva* najglasnije. (When she's in company, she always sings the loudest.)
6. *Pevaj* pesmu koju voliš, ne brini se šta drugi misle. (Sing the song you love, don't worry about what others think.)
7. Čuli smo kako *peva* golub na grani. (We heard the pigeon singing on the branch.)
8. On je glavni *pevač* u bendu. (He is the main singer in the band.)
9. Na koncertu je bilo mnogo ljudi koji su zajedno *pevali* omiljene pesme. (At the concert, there were many people who sang their favorite songs together.)
10. Ukoliko *pevate* svakodnevno, vaš glas će se poboljšati. (If you sing every day, your voice will improve.)